    "qualifications": "I'm an educator and developer in the Cardano ecosystem. I host the Learn Cardano Podcast, run the ADAOZ stake pool, and created the CardanoPress plugin to help projects integrate with WordPress. With a background in web development, I focus on making Cardano more accessible through clear, community-focused content. As a DRep, I aim to support decentralised governance, vote with transparency, and ensure treasury decisions reflect the long-term interests of the ecosystem.",
